messages.messageBody:
My friend, Ken, is a writing professor at Pima Community College here in
Tucson, AZ
He has 2 honors students who are interested in the transition from
homeschooling to college.
They've put together a survey and I've agreed to help them get it out to
the homeschooling community.

Feel free to forward to anyone you think would be interested.

Thanks!

Heather McLean
.....................................

Our project is on the transition from home school to college, so the survey
is for home schooled students who ARE attending college. The parents
perspective is also relevant so both students and families would be ideal
to reply to the survey. It is an online survey that shouldn't take
longer than 10 minutes.

Here is the URL if you would like to check it out.
http://www.surveymonkey.com/s/GGNNMHC

If you have any questions, feel free to email Emily at ejl0111@...

Thank you!
Emily and Kelsey
